 and they were brought up by somebody who I always referred to as an aunt, but in fact was a Dr. Barnardo\rquote 
s girl who looked after the family when my grandfather vanished. So I knew her, and I knew her as a member of the family. But the grandparents I didn\rquote t know at all, except my grandmother on my mother\rquote s side. That\rquote s all.
