 he was fairly late for my mother. But the two of us were very close, I think. We would play bridge together and we did a lot of climbing together \endash  at least, he did the climbing, I did the walking! I\rquote 
m a valley man! But we went out together, and we travelled together, clearly, as children. And, you know, we were at the same schools, we were at the same College in the University. He was a Fellow here. He went to Cambridge, 
Massachusetts, and I stayed here. Oh yes, we were quite close. And even now we\rquote re quite close.
