any. And then that seemed the last resort, and that\rquote s where I, with my friends Fisher, and Smith-Dorrien, and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid14039528 Edward}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid677667\charrsid677667  we broke out of a train and escaped up the hillside as we were being taken by Germans up to Germany. But that\rquote s the moment I recounted in t
hat account which appears in French and Italian.
