ontinued to hide in the river, and walked up the river in the other direction and got away across the road, and got in a little wood, met up with a Scotsman who\rquote 
d done the same thing, and we spent the night in this wood, and realised we were free again. And after that, I was free for the next four or five months.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid14039528   }{
