\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid677667\charrsid677667 Sanusi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid677667\charrsid677667  book.
\par 
