 29.16) I think, which was a very special school, and come back. And, anyhow, he knew a great deal about the area, so he oriented me, and he orientated}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid353933  (??)}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid677667\charrsid677667  me and suggested I should go down to this place that I eventually went to, called Birifu, which is about 10 miles, 15 miles away from there.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid1191190\charrsid1191190 Paul:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid677667\charrsid677667 \tab 
Did you tell him what kind of place you were looking for?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid1191190\charrsid1191190 Jack:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid677667\charrsid677667 \tab 
Well, in a sense, I suppose. But I found myself in a bit of a hornets\rquote  nest up there because I was looking to work in a certain tribe, a certain group, who had \endash  Fortes had worked in a strictly patrilineal society, and he wanted me, and I w
anted to work in something different, and this one was on the western border of Ghana, and it was partially matrilineal. As I say, it had matrilineal inheritance of moveable goods, [which] went to a man\rquote s sister\rquote 
s children, his cattle did, his wealth did. And I wanted to go there.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid1191190\charrsid1191190 Paul:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid677667\charrsid677667 \tab 
So you knew that beforehand, that it was partly matrilineal?
\par 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri113\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin113\lin1871\itap0\pararsid6181342 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid1191190\charrsid1191190 Jack:}{
