 how can I describe it? I didn\rquote t find any fixed terminology for peoples. It was as if }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid2645254 there were two terms \endash  one was \lquote Lobi\rquote }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid677667\charrsid677667 , that I wanted, because they were matrilineal,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid2645254 
 and the other ones were \lquote Dagarti\rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid677667\charrsid677667  \endash  but they changed, and sometimes, if you asked in an area, they would say, \'93
Yes, those people over there, they are Lobi\'94, or \'93Those people over there, they are Dagarti\'94, and if you asked about certain things, like matrilineal inheritance, then mat}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
