. It wasn\rquote t fixed, and therefore it changed. It was ... they used the te}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid2645254 rm something like people do as \lquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
