 seems to me, on perpetual retreat, mostly in North Wales, and has two children, two daughters, who are a bit more with it, as far as the world is concerned!}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid14092304   }{
