. One experiment he did was to sit his students round in a semi-circle, give them a story at one end, and asked them to repeat it to the next one and so on, round to the end, 
and it turned out to be something really different at the end than it was at the beginning. Well, that was an education which I should have thought of before when I first wrote the first account of the Bagre that I did, I wrote it as if it was a fixed acc
ount, more or less \endash 
