 a large amount of land and a plough \endash  where
as mine was going to inherit a small patch of land. So that seemed to me very important. That is what endeared me to Gordon Childe and the plough coming in Bronze Age society, and at the same time class divisions appearing \endash 
 economic class divisions appearing in an important sense, in that way.
