some Chinese there, and when I started talking }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid2914443 about the alphabet, they said, \'93}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
