tor there, and asking him about some words, and he went back to the Sanskrit roots. It meant something to him, going back to the Sanskrit roots of the words, even in this village. He would speak about this. So I wanted to see that, I wanted to see how the
 written civilisation worked out, the written culture worked out. 
\par 
