t seen them very often, but I\rquote ve seen them from to time. But to think that I\rquote ve been part of both the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid677667\charrsid677667 Past and Present}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid677667\charrsid677667 , and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid677667\charrsid677667 Comparative Studies in Society and History}{
